title: The Full Monty Actor Tom Wilkinson Dies Aged 75
description: Tom Wilkinson, the Oscar-nominated actor known for his roles in 'The Full Monty' and 'Michael Clayton' has died aged 75, his family said.

title: Biden Administration Bypasses Congress Again On Emergency Weapons Sale to Israel
description: For the second time this month the Biden administration is bypassing Congress to approve an emergency weapons sale to Israel.

title: Mark Zuckerberg Is Reportedly Building an Underground Bunker in Hawaii. Here’s What to Know
description: Meta's Mark Zuckerberg and his wife Priscilla Chan reportedly plan to build a 5,000-square-foot underground bunker on their Hawaii property.

title: California Is Expanding Health Care Coverage For Low-Income Immigrants in the New Year
description: More than 700,000 immigrants living illegally in California will gain access to free health care starting Monday.
